snippet.title: Mamono Musume: Life with a Lamia - Official English Trailer
snippet.description:
Published by JAST USA
Developed by Vanadis

Years ago, Light made a promise with his childhood crush, swearing that they would one day meet again to get married. Now, years later, he is surprised to find her standing on his doorstep, ready to pick back up where they left of! Only problem is... she isn't quite what he remembered.
